Package: asn
Title: ASN Brand Identity and Helper Functions 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Kurtis", "Pivert", , "kpivert@asn-online.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3428-2427"))
Description: Custom ggplot2 and highcharter functions for implementing ASN's 
    brand identity in data visualizations. Additional functions for calculating
    summaries for 'select all' survey questions and calculating percent changes
    are included.
